        <item>
            <title>支付宝系统错误自动 8 折，蚂蚁：不会追收差额、提防退款诈骗短讯</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/17/alipay-accidentally-20-percent-off/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=alipay-accidentally-20-percent-off</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/17/alipay-accidentally-20-percent-off/life-tech/epayment/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:00:37 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电子支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Alipay]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[支付宝]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[蚂蚁金融]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287527</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>支付宝昨日（16 日）因技术问题，导致部分订单价格自动调整为 8 折，并显示「政府补贴」讯息。事件引致系统出现大量交易金额异常，针对今次事故，蚂蚁集团已公开承诺承担全责，并明确表示不会向用户追讨折扣差额。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287529" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/e2978da9203f958c9992-520x580.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/e2978da9203f958c9992-520x580.jpg 520w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/e2978da9203f958c9992.jpg 807w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 520px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲漏洞发生期间出现「政府补贴」讯息，图片来源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2025-01-17/doc-ineffpzn3580049.shtml">新浪财经</a></p><p>昨日（17 日）下午 2 点 40 至 45 分期间，有用户使用支付宝交易时，因系统错误，支付金额自动 8 折，并显示「政府补贴」。经调查问题源于伺服器调整期间技术漏洞。尽管技术团队迅速修复系统，但已波及不少用户。支付宝发言人表示相关损失将由平台全数承担，用户毋须为此担忧。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287530" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1d0173c4043c53414f36-425x580.jpg" alt="" width="425" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1d0173c4043c53414f36-425x580.jpg 425w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1d0173c4043c53414f36.jpg 660w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 425px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲支付时显示「政府补贴」讯息，图片来源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2025-01-17/doc-ineffpzn3580049.shtml">新浪财经</a></p><p>支付宝亦发表声明，澄清所有「追回资金」的短讯均为诈骗，强调不会追回漏洞发生期间损失的金额，并呼吁市民提防受骗。声明澄清指：「支付宝官方没有发送任何资金追回短信，如果你收到了下图短信，千万不要点，以免上当受骗，也请大家帮忙相互转告。」</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287531" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011720910-628x580.jpg" alt="" width="628" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011720910-628x580.jpg 628w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025011720910.jpg 635w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 628px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲伪冒支付宝的诈骗短讯，图片来源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2025-01-17/doc-ineffpzn3580049.shtml">新浪财经</a></p><p>支付宝透露，是次事故是配合常规营销活动时误设营销模板，技术人员误值优惠额及类型，并再次重申不会向用户追回任何已发出的优惠。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287528" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/a3ca6f372f6f5a107693-220x580.jpg" alt="" width="220" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/a3ca6f372f6f5a107693-220x580.jpg 220w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/a3ca6f372f6f5a107693.jpg 342w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 220px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2025-01-17/doc-ineffpzn3580049.shtml">新浪财经</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2025-01-17/doc-ineffpzn3580049.shtml">新浪财经</a>、<a href="https://www.sohu.com/a/849918633_116062?scm=thor.521_14-200000.0.0.&amp;spm=smpc.home.it-news11.6.17370756000165oXoZw5_1467&amp;_trans_=060008_lym">搜狐</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
