            <title>LG 发布第四代 OLED 面板，亮度提升 33% 可达 4000 尼特</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/17/lg-announce-4th-gen-oled-panel/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lg-announce-4th-gen-oled-panel</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/17/lg-announce-4th-gen-oled-panel/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 03:00:16 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[4th Gen]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lg]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[OLED]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287464</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在今年的 CES，一向习惯推出新技术的 LG 却没有甚么大动作，正当大家以为 LG 在显示发展未有甚么新搞作的时候，近日就正式宣布推出他们的第四代 OLED 面板，当中采用了全新的 Primary RGB Tandem 架构，据指亮度比上代，即第三代 OLED 面板提升了 33%，即最高可达 4000 尼特。另外亦有不少新功能展现，想了解更多就要浏览内文了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287469" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_008-694x360.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="360" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_008-694x360.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_008.jpg 1013w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>LG 在新闻稿中发布最新第四代的 OLED 面板，它采用了全新的 Primary RGB Tandem 架构，据 LG 技术文件表示，相比第三代采用蓝-黄-蓝的三层架构，第四代 OLED 的 Primary RGB Tandem 架构将会设为四层，分别为红-蓝-绿-蓝架构，据官方指这个改动不但可以有效提升面板亮度，更可以令色准表现更佳。而更难得的是新面板不但令峰值亮度提升达 33%，同时功耗亦相应减低 20%，换言之在使用时将会更为省电。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287467" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_003-694x288.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="288" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_003-694x288.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_003.jpg 1198w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>此外，面板表面亦加入了全新的 Ultra anti-reflection 技术，据指可将高达 99% 的光线挡走，从而达到防反光的效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287468" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_015-694x283.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="283" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_015-694x283.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_015.jpg 1161w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>LG 亦表示第四代 OLED 面板的 DCI-P3 色域将达到 99.5%，而且在光或暗的环境，均可将真实的黑位呈现出来，令大家睇戏时不用拉窗帘，都可以有十分不错的观赏效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287470" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_004-694x290.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="290" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_004-694x290.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_004.jpg 1199w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287471" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_005-694x288.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="288" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_005-694x288.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_005.jpg 1199w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>官方亦指出这块第四代 OLED 面板将会应用在 48 吋至 83 吋的五个尺寸电视上，相信下半年大家应该会看到相关产品现身吧？</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287472" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_007-694x337.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="337" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_007-694x337.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lgdisplay_007.jpg 1116w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.lgdisplay.com/eng/company/media-center/latest-news?contentId=5372">LG Display</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
